node.text:
Top athletes from across the sports world will congregate tomorrow at the @arizonabiltmore for a two-day golf spectacular presented by Cannabis Now and Playbook Capital. ⁣⁣
⁣
Featured speakers include former #NBA star and @viola founder @alharrington3, Mina Mishrikey of Merida Capital and our very own #CannabisNow founder @eugeniocannabisnow. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Speakers and panel presentations will highlight investment and growth opportunities for athletes in the $50 billion #CBD + THC markets, while giving attendees the chance to #golf alongside and network with current and former professional athletes.⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⛳️ A big thank you to our title sponsor @fohse.inc. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Learn More: www.easygreens.live ⁣
⁣
#easygreensaz #cannabisnow #arizonabiltmore⁣ ⁣
⁣⁣
A portion of all funds raised will be donated to the Educational Sports Institute, an after school program for under-served communities. It's mission is to advance student athletes into well-rounded role models and contributing leaders to society.⁣

node.text:
With the help of the @fohse.inc team, Howard outfitted a #growroom at @thegrove_nevada with A3i fixtures to test the new technology. ⁣
⁣
The fall/winter 2020 #harvest results show that the Fohse A3i delivered 27% more light (as measured by PPFD, or photosynthetic photon flux density) than the facility’s HPS lamps. 💡 This led to a 65% increase in dry yield harvest weight. ⁣
⁣
Energy used for lighting was also reduced by 16%, with additional savings realized by a reduction in HVAC system use. ⁣
⁣
🌱read more about #cannabiscultivation at link in bio ⁣
🖊 A.J. Herrington for #CannabisNow⁣
📷 @keene.media ⁣
